          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " the telescope which consists of a sandwich of",
                "three parallel plate avalanche counters P1-P3, three",
                "multiwire proportional counters (two of which are used",
                "in parallel) D1 and D2 and an angular filter which",
                "defines the direction of the recoil particles within",
                "+-3.8 degr. in the scaterring plane and within 14.degr",
                "in the plane perpendicular to the scaterring plane.",
                "The essential features of the counter elements are:",
